---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../../styles/global.css';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="AI Tools for Small Business — 50+ Tools Ranked and Reviewed (2026) | xSoft Blog" description="The definitive list of AI tools for small businesses in 2026. 50+ tools ranked across 10 categories — writing, customer support, marketing, design, development, analytics, and more. Free options included." keywords="AI tools small business, best AI tools 2026, AI for SMEs, business AI software, AI productivity tools, free AI tools for business">

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "AI Tools for Small Business — 50+ Tools Ranked and Reviewed (2026)",
    "description": "The definitive list of AI tools for small businesses in 2026. 50+ tools ranked across 10 categories with pricing and use cases.",
    "datePublished": "2026-07-19",
    "dateModified": "2026-07-19",
    "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Raj Naik", "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com/about/" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "xSoft Ltd", "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com/social-card.svg" } },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.xsoftlimited.com/blog/ai-tools-small-business/" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What AI tools should a small business start with?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Start with three: ChatGPT or Claude for writing and research, Canva AI for design, and a basic chatbot for your website. These cover the highest-impact use cases (content creation, visual assets, customer support) with minimal cost and learning curve." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much do AI tools cost for a small business?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Many AI tools offer free tiers sufficient for small businesses. Paid plans typically range from £10-50/month per tool. A comprehensive AI toolkit (writing + design + analytics + support) costs £100-300/month total — less than a single part-time hire." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Are AI tools safe for business data?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most major AI tools (ChatGPT Business, Claude, Gemini) offer enterprise-grade security and don't train on your data. Always check: data retention policies, GDPR compliance, SOC 2 certification, and whether your inputs are used for model training. For sensitive data, self-hosted or edge-deployed options (like Cloudflare Workers AI) keep data on your infrastructure." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can AI tools replace employees?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "AI tools augment employees rather than replace them. They handle repetitive tasks (drafting emails, generating social posts, answering FAQs) so your team can focus on strategy, relationships, and creative work. Most businesses find AI makes existing employees 30-50% more productive rather than making them redundant." }},
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "Which AI tools have the best free tiers?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Best free tiers in 2026: ChatGPT (GPT-4o mini, generous limits), Canva (AI design features included free), Google Gemini (free access to capable model), HubSpot CRM (free with AI features), Notion AI (limited free), and Cloudflare Workers AI (100K free inference requests/month)." }}
    ]
  })} />

  <section class="pt-10 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">AI Tools for Business</span>
      </nav>

      <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20">AI Tools</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20">Small Business</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20">Listicle</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20">2026 Ranked</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-white leading-tight">AI Tools for Small Business — 50+ Tools Ranked and Reviewed (2026)</h1>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
            <time datetime="2026-07-19">19 July 2026</time>
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
            <span>20 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">The AI tool landscape in 2026 is overwhelming. Hundreds of tools launch monthly, each claiming to revolutionise your business. Most are wrappers around the same few models. A handful are genuinely transformative.</p>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">We've tested, deployed, and integrated AI tools for businesses across the UK. This isn't a list scraped from Product Hunt — it's a practitioner's guide based on what actually works in production, what delivers ROI, and what's worth your time.</p>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Each tool is scored on: usefulness for small businesses, ease of setup, pricing fairness, and whether it genuinely leverages AI (vs just marketing). We've organised by category so you can jump to what matters for your business.</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-8 p-5 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 bg-indigo-950/20">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">📋 Categories Covered</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
            <p>1. Writing & Content</p>
            <p>2. Customer Support</p>
            <p>3. Design & Creative</p>
            <p>4. Marketing & SEO</p>
            <p>5. Development & Code</p>
            <p>6. Analytics & Data</p>
            <p>7. Sales & CRM</p>
            <p>8. Operations & Automation</p>
            <p>9. Voice & Audio</p>
            <p>10. Infrastructure & AI APIs</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 1: Writing -->
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">1. Writing & Content Creation</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">The most mature AI category. These tools help with everything from blog posts to email copy to documentation.</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">ChatGPT (OpenAI)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 9/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">The gold standard for general writing, research, brainstorming, and problem-solving. GPT-4o handles complex tasks; GPT-4o mini is fast and cheap for routine work. New Canvas feature is excellent for collaborative writing.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (GPT-4o mini) | Plus: $20/month | Team: $25/user/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Blog drafts, email copy, product descriptions, research summaries, brainstorming</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Claude (Anthropic)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 9/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Excellent for longer documents, careful analysis, and nuanced writing. Better than ChatGPT at following complex instructions and maintaining consistency across long outputs. Artifacts feature is great for iterative work.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (limited) | Pro: $20/month | Team: $25/user/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Long-form content, strategy documents, reports, careful analysis, technical writing</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Jasper</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Paid only</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Marketing-focused AI writer with brand voice training, templates for common formats (ads, social, email), and team collaboration. Overpiced for what you get vs ChatGPT/Claude, but the templates save time for marketing teams.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $49/month (Creator) | Team: $125/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Marketing teams needing consistent brand voice across channels</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Grammarly</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">AI-powered writing assistant that works everywhere (email, docs, browser). Tone detection, clarity suggestions, and full rewrite capabilities. The browser extension is genuinely useful for every team member.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (basic) | Premium: £12/month | Business: £15/user/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Non-writers who need professional communication (everyone on your team)</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Notion AI</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">AI built into your workspace. Summarise meeting notes, draft content, brainstorm in context. Best feature: it has access to all your Notion docs, so it can answer questions about your own knowledge base.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Included with Notion Plus ($10/user/month)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams already using Notion who want AI on their existing content</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 2: Customer Support -->
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">2. Customer Support & Chatbots</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">AI that handles customer queries, deflects tickets, and provides 24/7 availability without hiring night staff.</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Intercom (Fin AI Agent)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Premium</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 9/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Best-in-class AI support agent. Fin resolves 50%+ of conversations without human intervention. Trains on your help centre, understands context, and seamlessly escalates when needed. Expensive but high ROI.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $0.99 per AI resolution + platform ($65+/month)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> SaaS companies and e-commerce with high support volume</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Tidio</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Affordable live chat + AI chatbot combo. The Lyro AI chatbot learns from your FAQ content and resolves basic queries automatically. Good for small e-commerce stores that need something functional without a big budget.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (basic) | Starter: $29/month | Lyro AI: $39/month add-on</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Small e-commerce stores needing affordable AI chat</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Custom RAG Chatbot (e.g., xSoft-built)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20">Custom</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 9/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Purpose-built chatbot trained on YOUR data, deployed on YOUR infrastructure. No monthly platform fees, full data ownership, unlimited customisation. Higher upfront cost but best long-term economics and quality.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> £8-25K build + £200-500/month running costs</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Businesses wanting full control, data ownership, and premium quality</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Freshdesk (Freddy AI)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Full helpdesk with AI-powered ticket routing, suggested responses, and basic chatbot. Good mid-market option if you need a helpdesk anyway. AI features are add-ons to the core product.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (basic) | Growth: $15/agent/month | Pro: $49/agent/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Growing teams that need helpdesk + AI in one platform</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Zendesk (AI Agents)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Paid only</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Enterprise-grade helpdesk with powerful AI. Excellent for larger teams with complex routing needs. AI features include auto-classification, suggested responses, and autonomous resolution. Pricey for small teams.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $55/agent/month (Suite Team)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Established businesses with 5+ support agents needing enterprise features</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 3: Design -->
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">3. Design & Creative</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Generate images, edit photos, create presentations, and produce design assets without a professional designer.</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Canva (Magic Studio)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 9/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">The best all-in-one design tool for non-designers. AI features: text-to-image generation, background removal, magic resize, design suggestions, and brand kit consistency. Genuinely usable by anyone.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (generous) | Pro: £10/month | Teams: £12.50/user/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Social media graphics, presentations, marketing materials, quick design work</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Midjourney</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Paid only</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Best image quality for artistic and marketing visuals. Generates stunning imagery from text prompts. The v6 model produces photorealistic results. Web interface is now available (no more Discord-only).</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $10/month (Basic) | $30/month (Standard, recommended)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Blog hero images, social media visuals, concept art, brand imagery</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Adobe Firefly</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Adobe's AI image generator. Key advantage: commercially safe (trained on licensed/Adobe Stock content). Integrated into Photoshop and Illustrator for generative fill/expand. Less artistic than Midjourney but safer for commercial use.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (25 credits/month) | Creative Cloud includes full access</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Businesses needing commercially-safe AI-generated imagery</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Figma AI</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">AI features within Figma: auto-layout suggestions, design-to-code generation, visual search, and smart selection. Best for teams already using Figma for UI/UX design. AI generates UI components from text descriptions.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (limited) | Professional: $15/editor/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Product teams doing UI/UX design who want AI-assisted workflows</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Remove.bg</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">Does one thing perfectly: removes image backgrounds using AI. Incredibly accurate, even with complex hair/fur edges. Essential for product photography, headshots, and any compositing work.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free (low-res) | Pay-as-you-go: from £0.90/image | Subscription: £8/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> E-commerce product photos, team headshots, marketing materials</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Category 4: Marketing & SEO -->
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">4. Marketing & SEO</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Tools that help you reach more customers, rank higher on Google, and produce marketing content at scale.</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Surfer SEO</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Paid only</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">AI-powered content optimisation. Analyses top-ranking pages for your keyword and tells you exactly what to include: word count, headings, keywords, and structure. The Content Editor gives a real-time score as you write.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $89/month (Essential) | Scale: $129/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> Businesses investing seriously in organic search and content marketing</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">SEMrush (AI Writing)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/20">Paid only</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 8/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">All-in-one SEO platform with AI content generation, keyword research, site audits, and competitor analysis. The ContentShake AI feature generates full articles optimised for target keywords. Expensive but comprehensive.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Pricing:</strong> From $130/month (Pro) | Guru: $250/month</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500"><strong>Best for:</strong> SEO-focused businesses needing comprehensive keyword and competitor data</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 bg-gray-900/30">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
              <p class="text-white font-semibold">Buffer (AI Assistant)</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">Free tier</span>
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">⭐ 7/10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
